snippet.title: SAGE 2024 - FIGHTING VIPERS HONEY RELEASE
snippet.description:
This will be the release of the first part of the Fighting Vipers Update of Sonic The Fighters Blitz Hyper Edition. It will be released at the Sonic Amateur Games Expo this year. The Update will be available to download at our Gamejolt and SAGE Booth.

Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/BlitzHyperEdition/816407
SAGE: -TBA-
Twitter: https://twitter.com/STFB_HE
